{"tid":1605720,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"路透：外交官消息 駐港解放軍增1倍至1.2萬人","createTime":"2019-09-30T11:15:35.000Z","updateTime":"2019-09-30T14:12:12.000Z","uid":68738,"like":4,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":14,"replies":[{"pid":"354340b0f261f666a7e3670a61ff9cf15846eaf1","tid":1605720,"uid":68738,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-30T11:15:36.000Z","msg":"路透社今日（30日）引述多個駐港外交官透露，目前有1.2萬名解放軍駐紮香港，比原來增加一倍。除了解放軍之外，內地武警已準備就緒聽令國家主席習近平的指揮，一旦北京政府介入香港平息衝突，他們將會執行任務。<br />\n<br />\n報道指，北京上月已將逾千軍隊駐紮只有一河之隔的深圳，他們有乘船、大巴、火車，以及裝甲車抵埗。新華社形容行動是「例行任務」，沒有提及由6月至今震動社會的反政府示威。當中，有非正式報告指中國在香港已維持一定數量的軍力，路透社早前取得特首林鄭月娥與本地商家的錄音顯示，中國「肯定沒有計劃」動用解放軍平息衝突。<br />\n<br />\n不過，路透社表示，過去一個月來，在香港的亞洲和西方使節指，解放軍在8月底已進行非常規佈防，7名使節向路透社稱，他們未能偵查到目前在港有多少軍力已退回中國；當中有3名使節稱，在港的解放軍隊伍自示威開始已增加了一倍，估計數量由3,000至5,000人增加至1萬至1.2萬之間。使節相信，中國已在香港大規模部署解放軍、反暴警力和裝備。<br />\n<br />\n5名使節稱，負責維護內地安全和控制群眾的武警已經在港成形，與解放軍不同，他們聽取不同的指揮，而路透社未能肯定武警的規模，但使節指，在港的軍力大部份來自解放軍。<br />\n<br />\n路透社記者到多個駐紮香港的解放軍軍營觀察，明顯軍隊和裝甲車的移動有所增加。中國國防部、國務院新聞辦和港澳辦則拒絕回應路透社的提問，但9月初，港澳辦發言人曾表示，如果香港持續威脅「國家主權」，中國不會「坐視不理」。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://hk.news.appledaily.com/china/realtime/article/20190930/60101726\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Fchina%2Frealtime%2Farticle%2F20190930%2F60101726&d=l0hx0y7EoyLX%2BzZhnd86Zo6aL69TDc1SPHZju%2B%2BXLiQ%3D&h=bffef991\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Fchina%2Frealtime%2Farticle%2F20190930%2F60101726&h=bd23a259\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.news.appledaily.com/china/realtime/article/20190930/60101726</a>"},{"pid":"662f72d85599faf051db16a5e453b236cbe26ffd","tid":1605720,"uid":297230,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-30T11:19:25.000Z","msg":"Telegram 預設訊息可以保護到手足性命<br />\n希望大家可以幫手推<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/kCXiwqP.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FkCXiwqP.png&h=5c04cb99&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n星火 TG: @Abccbbc<br />\n612 TG: @ReliefFund612<br />\nPush"},{"pid":"43e1baa2ff00d61504caca3ca264db9b0167c705","tid":1605720,"uid":121961,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-30T11:32:21.000Z","msg":"快出<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/biggrin.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3efc1fa23f57e41904b3ba818ce35a382329b6fe","tid":1605720,"uid":274435,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-30T11:33:46.000Z","msg":"唔夠棉被<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5f758f95922669669b8bd8b6216fc879a1c51ca3","tid":1605720,"uid":52090,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-30T11:36:15.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4cd9d32c0757df13b773643bff93bae3f24a85b6","tid":1605720,"uid":254594,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-09-30T11:46:09.000Z","msg":"多出既駐軍住邊？<br />\n斷估唔會住中聯辦物業咁優待佢地"},{"pid":"7e4c0be7d46df49879db853b28efd076d8af266d","tid":1605720,"uid":76216,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-30T11:46:55.000Z","msg":"怕你麼"},{"pid":"7444454e3d2786dcc024391203db3b5ee7b99e96","tid":1605720,"uid":198035,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-30T13:58:55.000Z","msg":"."},{"pid":"91a5116f2c10fef8e8d0b391ea4d6566ae937d2d","tid":1605720,"uid":55923,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-30T13:59:45.000Z","msg":"多咗6000張被<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/scare.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/scare.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/scare.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"16ff0dc694c22d66400cc8ed8323900503495da5","tid":1605720,"uid":244034,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"4cd9d32c0757df13b773643bff93bae3f24a85b6","tid":1605720,"uid":254594,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-09-30T11:46:09.000Z","msg":"多出既駐軍住邊？<br />\n斷估唔會住中聯辦物業